            "jpText": "屋上へ行くと、難しい顔をした\nステイゴールドと遭遇した。\nなにか悩みごとかと、声をかけると……。",
            "enText": "On the rooftop, I encountered Stay Gold \nmaking a difficult expression. As I asked \nwhat was on her mind…",
