        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "やー、なんだか今日は、\n朝からすごく眠くてな。\n授業も丸一日サボっちまった……ふぁ……。",
            "enText": "Yea, I was like really sleepy from the \nmorning today. I even ended up \nskipping the entire day of class… \n<i>Fuaa…</i>",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 102,
            "voiceIdx": 105,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "それは……寝すぎだな！",
                    "enText": "That is… way too much sleep!",
                    "nextBlock": 5
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "それは……寝すぎだね！",
                    "enText": "That is… way too much sleep!",
                    "nextBlock": 5
                }
