        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "寝たいときに寝て、\n起きたいときに起きるのが――",
            "enText": "When you're sleepy you sleep, and when \nyou want to wake up you get up so —",
